%% Diagram: State Taxonomy
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TB
    Local["Local / UI state<br/><br/>forms, focus, layout toggles<br/>URL when address bar is truth"]
    Global["Coordinating client state<br/><br/>session shell, theme, flags<br/>narrow write APIs"]
    Server["Server-backed cache<br/><br/>truth on origin; client caches<br/>staleness + invalidation rules"]
    Derived["Derived state<br/><br/>pure projection of inputs<br/>select / memoize, never write"]

    Local -->|"shared write path"| Global
    Local -->|"needs authority"| Server
    Server -->|"hydrates cache"| Global
    Local -.->|read model| Derived
    Global -.->|read model| Derived
    Server -.->|read model| Derived
